Date: 1995-03-07

Title: Non-Abelian Duality and Canonical Transformations

Comments: 9 pags, latex file

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B355 (1995) 165-170

We construct explicit canonical transformations producing non-abelian duals inprincipal chiral models with arbitrary group G. Some comments concerning theextension to more general $\sigma$-models, like WZW models, are given.